      "text": "1. **Enhanced PlanMetadata Interface:** Added request context fields (`request_id`, `request_title`, `request_agent`, `request_portal`, `request_priority`, `request_created_by`)\n2. **Request Data Loading:** Modified `PlanCommands.extractPlanMetadataWithRequest()` to load request information when `request_id` is present in plan frontmatter\n3. **CLI Display Updates:** Updated `exactl plan list` and `exactl plan show` commands to display request context information\n4. **Config Path Fix:** Corrected workspace path configuration in `exa.config.toml` (removed redundant `./Workspace/` prefixes)\n5. **Title Extraction:** Implemented smart title extraction from request content (prefers headers, falls back to first content line)\n\n**Files Modified:**",
